      "id": "PopularPost215626",
      "post_content": "A solid r/w land. In the first few turns it might sting a little, but once you get a few more lands on the field it provides colorless mana readily.  \n  \nIn most games, I don't lose any life with it (since I use it for its colorless mana), but occasionally I let it sting me for 1 or 2 points of damage while I'm waiting for my mana colors to be fixed. If I have 4 lands on the field, I usually only need to use this to pump my creatures enchanted with a [Scourge of the Nobilis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scourge of the Nobilis), which is fine because I get the life I gave up right back.",
      "posted_by": "Asmodi0000",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost215626\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">A solid r/w land. In the first few turns it might sting a little, but once you get a few more lands on the field it provides colorless mana readily.<br/><br/>In most games, I don't lose any life with it (since I use it for its colorless mana), but occasionally I let it sting me for 1 or 2 points of damage while I'm waiting for my mana colors to be fixed. If I have 4 lands on the field, I usually only need to use this to pump my creatures enchanted with a <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scourge of the Nobilis\">Scourge of the Nobilis</a>, which is fine because I get the life I gave up right back.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18984\">Asmodi0000</span>\r\n                                (12/10/2011 7:14:08 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><i